SYSTEMS MANAGER

- Visibility and control over your aws resources

- Inventory of your ec2 instances

- Automation
  - Installing apps
  - Script execution
  - Patching
  - Logically group resources

  - Run command: perform operational tasks


AUTOMATING PATCHING USING SYSTEMS MANAGER

- Create an IAM role
  - amazonec2roleforssm

- attach the role to the ec2 instance

- select fleet manager in ssm

- select patch manager

- check the baseline patch 

RUN COMMAND
